{"tid":2280490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國失業率升至4.8%     反映武漢肺炎疫情持續打擊勞動市場","createTime":"2020-11-10T13:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T13:47:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"401b898ee2d1422aadd66611855cf353379df546","tid":2280490,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:45:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559302-20201110.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559302-20201110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=c20f6cbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559302-20201110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=be480f43\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559302-20201110.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國失業率由4.5%升至4.8%，並錄得超過31萬4千個職位流失，反映武漢肺炎疫情持續打擊勞動市場。<br />\n<br />\n市場早已對就業情況抱持悲觀預期，因為當地以保就業為目標的休假計劃補貼，原定上月底結束，增加僱主在期限前刪減職位的誘因。<br />\n<br />\n政府早前宣布，將休假計劃有效期延長至明年3月底，但分析師認為決定來得太遲，趕不及挽救職位，又預期在未來幾個月，失業率有機會進一步攀升。"},{"pid":"1536f7ba73b6afb6dff466f2694d8d3e5a279ef4","tid":2280490,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:47:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">英國最新失業率4.8%   法國第3季失業率升至9%</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559251-20201110.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559251-20201110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=2eb1ed38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559251-20201110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=184baa47\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559251-20201110.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國截至9月的3個月，按國際勞工組織(ILO)標準計算，失業率4.8%，符合預期。<br />\n<br />\n至上月的裁員人數升至31.4萬人，創新高，10月申領失業金人數按月減少近3萬人。<br />\n<br />\n統計局表示，近期裁員人數創紀錄新高，自今年3月以來，登記在薪資冊上勞工數量減少逾78萬人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，法國國家統計局公布，第3季失業率由第2季7.1%升至9%。"}]}